text: hmmmm... Wondering if I'm approaching this week's article incorrectly.

Originally I was just gonna talk about the new Rakdos toys for Mass Discard Xantcha, but with [[Captive Audience]] and [[Theater of Horrors]] both being pseudo-copies of Xantcha in the deck, I wonder if I should be going about it from the premise of "why you should play multiple effects that do what your commander does"
